                  <p>Despite different scales/regions, COMMON STRATEGIC GOAL: Seek direct link with peasant to: (1) MAXIMIZE REVENUE‚Äîeliminate intermediary leakage. (2) ENSURE FAIRNESS‚Äîprotect peasant from arbitrary exploitation (ensures long-term productivity). (3) BUILD LOYALTY‚Äîfairly-treated peasant = loyal subject supporting state vs. rebels/invaders. (4) CREATE SUSTAINABILITY‚Äîprosperous peasantry = sustainable revenue stream. Revenue administration = foundation of state power in agricultural economy. All three rulers understood: Fair treatment of cultivator = enlightened self-interest, not just morality.</p>
